summary: Eclipse has a lesser known Dusk form that is in need of artwork, so I decided to draw some to add to her collection of art. Her...
caption:
Eclipse has a lesser known Dusk form that is in need of artwork, so I decided to draw some to add to her collection of art.

Her Dusk form is something she can physically change into (unlike her illusions)at dusk and can remain in throughout the night. However, she does shift back in the morning and cannot access this form during the day.


Character, art: @eyesorefortheblind

summary:
Hello, and welcome to this new experiment I'm trying out. Once a 
day, everyday for the foreseeable future, I am going to draw...
caption:
Hello, and welcome to this new experiment I’m trying out. Once a day, everyday for the foreseeable future, I am going to draw one character and upload them here. They can be OC’s, other peoples OC’s, Creatures, characters from movies and Tv, ect. I might take requests down the road if I actually keep up with this, we’ll see.
Mimikyu from Pokemon: Sun and Moon
I know most people like the version of Mimikyu that’s more sweeter and wants to fit it, but I personally more enjoy the Anime’s take on it where it’s just a tiny ball of loathing and contempt. Both are good though! For yet another Pikachu knockoff, this one’s pretty good!
